TY  - JOUR
T1  - Quadratic Approximations of the Portfolio Selection Problem When the Means and Variances of Returns are Infinite
AU  - Ohlson, James A.
Y1  - 1977/02/01
PY  - 1977
DA  - 1977/02/01
